Large fixed file formats

In this assignment we will work with large fixed file formats from Centers of Disease Control and Prevention (CDC). Since the files are so huge we used a fixed file format read to extract only the columns we needed. The data was persisted to a file named extracted- with only the data we needed. This reduced the file size drastically.
